                Our day wouldn’t be the same without that first cup of coffee in the morning. The fresh aroma and bitter taste get us ready to tackle what lies ahead. But the benefits of coffee aren’t limited to just that. You’ve probably seen an increasing number of hair care products that use caffeine as an ingredient - and there’s a really good reason why. Let’s dive into why caffeine spiked products are all the rage right now, we’re here to spill the beans about the benefits of coffee for your hair.
            </p>
            
